data.description: Privacy, acreage & views! This wonderful nautical designed home has a stunning water view from almost every room. The perfect blend of comfort, privacy, and convenience, it is only 10 minutes from town on a spacious 3+ acre lot with no restrictions. Additional features include a detached garage, outbuilding, & two gardens for food & beauty. There is a 1-bedroom guest cottage for hosting guests or generating extra income & it is close to parks, the Discovery Trail, beaches & the boat launch.
